        "Autonomous coordinate-based navigation",
        "GPS + IMU + AHRS sensor fusion",
        "Stepper motor based propulsion system",
        "Real-time GUI control and monitoring",
        "Vision-based obstacle detection",
        "High accuracy marking (~±1 cm)",
        "Spray mechanism synchronized with position coordinates"
